lead_paragraph: Tony Graziani threw six touchdown passes — three to Chris Jackson — to help the Philadelphia Soul beat the visiting Dragons, 63-42, in the Arena Football League. Aaron Garcia threw 6 touchdowns passes for the Dragons (1-2). Kevin Swayne had seven receptions for 84 yards and 3 touchdowns.
